data.description: EXPLORE THE RICH HISTORY of this farmhouse set on a .74 acre corner lot on Freedom Road, a part of the Underground Railroad. Embrace the opportunity to infuse your personal style and preferences into the living spaces, which feature  hardwood and wood floors, living room with fireplace, brand new 1st floor full bath, front enclosed porch, and a 1st floor laundry. Revel in the tranquility of Loyalsock country living with the convenience of being just minutes from all the amenities of the City of Williamsport. Intrigued? Contact Lise Barrick for your personal tour! 570-847-4775.
